verbose_text: Regarding the effect on specific B-lymphocyte subtypes, a significant increase in circulating total CD19 + B cells and mature-naive CD27 - CD38 - IgD + B cells was observed with spebrutinib versus placebo at week 4 (P < 0.05), whereas levels of transitional CD27 - CD38 + B cells significantly decreased with spebrutinib versus placebo at the same time point (P < 0.05).
